column26: My sister is a teacher (Missouri). She says it is all the hand sanitizer. Also, all the teachers in her district were named TEACHER OF THE YEAR in 2020. That definitely helped. Also, the MO AG has sued to prevent all mitigation & meaningful reporting.

column3: @RadioFreeTom There’s a school district near me that has no mask mandate and 2 teachers have died. Yet because of political reasons no one will institute a mask mandate. School Board maths are a mess everywhere in Missouri
